snippet.title: UpRunner.io - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
New game!

Uprunner is a free-to-play MMO vertical speedrunner.

Win lobbies or create your own maps to earn coins and unlock unique randomly generated skins!

Game Features:
- Lobby with all the players on the same map changing every 5 minutes!
- Level editor with many blocks and skins to try
- Hundreds of community maps already available!
- Climb the leaderboard and show the world your skills!
- Unique skin generation inspired by CS:GO
- Unlock new profile customization elements by playing!
- Unique level up system based on players trading

You can play for free now on Steam or Itch.io:
- https://store.steampowered.com/app/3251630/UpRunner_Demo/
- https://zeksa.itch.io/uprunner

Thank you for your support ^-^
